#
# ui_agents_fabric.py:
#   - PROJECT_ENDPOINT ✓ (必要)
#   - MODEL_DEPLOYMENT_NAME ✓ (必要)
#   - FABRIC_CONNECTION_NAME ✓ (必要 - 使用真實 Fabric 連接)
#
# sample_agents_fabric.py (參考範例):
#   - PROJECT_ENDPOINT ✓ (必要)
#   - MODEL_DEPLOYMENT_NAME ✓ (必要)
#   - FABRIC_CONNECTION_NAME ✓ (必要)
#
# 圖例 (Legend):
# ✓ = 必要 (Required)
# ○ = 選用 (Optional)
#
# ============================================================================
# 範例值 (Example Values)
# ============================================================================
#
# 以下是完整的範例設定供參考 (不要直接使用):
# Below is a complete example configuration for reference (DO NOT use directly):
#
# 基本設定 (Basic Configuration):
# PROJECT_ENDPOINT=https://my-ai-project.cognitiveservices.azure.com/
