# AZURE_TENANT_ID=12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789abc
# AZURE_CLIENT_ID=87654321-4321-4321-4321-123456789abc
# AZURE_CLIENT_SECRET=your-client-secret-here
#
# ============================================================================
# 重要提醒 (Important Notes)
# ============================================================================
#
# 1. 真實 Fabric 連接 (Real Fabric Connection):
#    - 必須設定 FABRIC_CONNECTION_NAME
#    - 在 Azure AI Foundry 中建立並配置 Fabric 連接
#    - 確保 Fabric lakehouse 包含所需的數據表
#    - Must set FABRIC_CONNECTION_NAME
#    - Create and configure Fabric connection in Azure AI Foundry
#    - Ensure Fabric lakehouse contains required data tables
#
# 2. Fabric 連接設定步驟 (Fabric Connection Setup):
#    - 在 Azure AI Foundry 專案中，前往 "Connected resources"
#    - 點擊 "New connection" > "Microsoft Fabric"
#    - 選擇您的 Fabric workspace 和 lakehouse
#    - 設定權限並儲存連接
#    - 複製連接名稱到環境變數
#    - In Azure AI Foundry project, go to "Connected resources"
#    - Click "New connection" > "Microsoft Fabric"
#    - Select your Fabric workspace and lakehouse
#    - Configure permissions and save connection
#    - Copy connection name to environment variable
#
# 3. 認證方式 (Authentication):
#    - 開發環境: 使用 az login (最簡單)
#    - 生產環境: 使用 Managed Identity (最安全)
#    - CI/CD: 使用 Service Principal (環境變數)
#    - Development: Use az login (easiest)
#    - Production: Use Managed Identity (most secure)
#    - CI/CD: Use Service Principal (environment variables)
#
# 4. 權限檢查 (Permission Check):
#    - 確認 AI Foundry 專案權限
#    - 確認 Fabric Workspace 訪問權限
#    - 確認 Lakehouse 讀取權限
#    - 參考租戶設定文件配置 Data Agent
#    - Verify AI Foundry project permissions
#    - Verify Fabric Workspace access
#    - Verify Lakehouse read permissions
#    - Configure Data Agent per tenant settings documentation
#
# ============================================================================
